165
00:18:04,380 --> 00:18:12,380
[SPEAKER_00] I mean, people didn't want to go to restaurants, people didn't want to fly, casinos, hotels, you name it.

166
00:18:12,380 --> 00:18:21,380
[SPEAKER_00] So, essentially, a large fraction of the workforce was basically asked or compelled to stay at home or the investment in public health.

167
00:18:21,380 --> 00:18:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] While others, like myself, for example, my colleagues were able to work from home.

168
00:18:25,380 --> 00:18:30,380
